(148, 4, 'BHUMI Acid Complex Clearing Serum', 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/product/detail/acid-complex-clearing-serum', 'BHUMI', 'Rp 307.050', 'Contains 2% BHA that is dramatically reduces oil production, unclogging pores and fight for acne bacteria. Also contains Acnatu Extract that plays important role to immediately remove bacteria causing acne. It is infused with borage oil which contains 3% Gamma Linoleic Acid as the skin soothing and anti-inflammatory agent that helps to maintain the stability and fluidity of the water loss barrier, and 4%linoleic Acid to unclog oil inside the pores and soothes irritants', 1, 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/assets/uploads/products/thumbs/800x800/Serum_actual_Acne.jpg\r'),
