(253, 3, 'DERMALUZ Hydrate Glow Daily Day Cream UV Filter', 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/product/detail/hydrate-glow-daily-day-cream-uv-filter', 'DERMALUZ ', 'Rp 63.000', 'Digunakan untuk melembabkan menghidrasi kulit wajah dan mencerahkan wajah,Â menyamarkan bekas acne dan flek di wajah, memberikan efek soothing, menghaluskanÂ pori wajah dan proteksi UV A dan UV B.', 0, 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/assets/uploads/products/thumbs/800x800/DERMALUZ_HYDRATE_GLOW_Dayli_Day_UV_Filter.png\r'),
(254, 3, 'DERMALUZ Hydrate Glow Night Cream', 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/product/detail/hydrate-glow-night-cream', 'DERMALUZ', 'Rp 67.000', 'Mencerahkan wajah, membuat warna kulit lebih merata, menghaluskan wajah, melembutkan wajah, menyamarkan noda atau flek wajah, dan melembabkan. Dapat direkomendasikan untuk kulit sensitif, menyamarkan pori-pori wajah dan antiaging.', 0, 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/assets/uploads/products/thumbs/800x800/Dermaluz_HYDRATE_GLOW_Night_Cream.png\r'),
(255, 3, 'DERMALUZ ProActive Acne Night Cream', 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/product/detail/proactive-acne-night-cream', 'DERMALUZ ', 'Rp 72.000', 'Bekerja aktif untuk kulit jerawat/ membantu proses penyembuhan jerawat mencerahkan wajah serta menyamarkan bekas jerawat, membuat warna kulit lebih merata, menyamarkan redmark, menghaluskan wajah, memberikan efek soothing, memperbaiki tekstur kulit wajah, mengecilkan pori-pori wajah, melembabkan tanpa membuat kulit berminyak dan non comedogenic formula.', 0, 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/assets/uploads/products/thumbs/800x800/DERMALUZ_Proactive_Acne_Night_Cream.png\r'),
(256, 4, ' DERMALUZ Lucem Smothees Power Serum with Galactomyces ', 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/product/detail/lucem-smothees-power-serum-with-galactomyces', 'DERMALUZ ', 'Rp 145.000', 'Diformulasikan dengan segala kebaikan Galactomyces Ferment Filtrate dengan sangat baik menjaga elassitas kulit, memperlambat proses penuaan kulit wajah, kandungan AHA dan BHA dengan cara kerja melakukan ekfoliasi ringan untuk kulit wajah, mempercepat regenerasi sel2 kulit baru, memperbaiki dan menghaluskan kulit wajah,mengontrol minyak berlebih pada wajah, kandungan Alpha-Arbun , Niacinamide berfungsi mencerahkan wajah membuat warna kulit lebih merata, mengurangi bekas jerawat dan flek2 hitam diwajah serta produk ini juga bekerja mencegah whiteheads, blackheads, memperbaiki skin barrier dan masalah pori-pori lainnya. Tetapi bisa digunakan untuk yang memiliki kulit kering karena memiliki manfaat hidrasi dari kandungan Chamomilla Recuta (Matricaria) Flower Extract, Sodium Hyaluronate, Ceramide NP selain berfungsi sebagai penyeimbang pH pada kulit wajah, LUCEM SMOTHEES POWER SERUM WITH GALACTOMYCES ini juga sebagai anaging, meningkatkan elassitas kulit.', 0, 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/assets/uploads/products/thumbs/800x800/DERMALUZ_LUCEM_SMOTHEES_POWER_SERUM_With_Galactomyces.png\r'),
(257, 5, 'DERMALUZ Hydrating Sunscreen ', 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/product/detail/hydrating-sunscreen', 'DERMALUZ', 'Rp 72.000', 'Digunakan untuk proteksi UV A dan UV B, mencerahkan wajah, membantu meratakan warna kulit wajah, menyamarkan pori - pori, melembabkan wajah, skin barrier repair. Digunakan untuk semua jenis kulit dan dapat direkomedasikan untuk kulit berjerawat.', 0, 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/assets/uploads/products/thumbs/800x800/Dermaluz_Hydrtating_Suncreen.png\r'),
(258, 5, 'Dew It Dew It On The Go - Sunscreen Mist ', 'https://www.sociolla.com/sun-care/59158-dew-it-on-the-go-sunscreen-mist', 'DEW IT', 'Rp 220.000', 'Takut akan kerusakan kulit yang di akibatkan oleh sinar matahari atau sun burns yang tidak diinginkan? Perkenalkan Sunscreen yang menutrisi kulit, mempunyai broad-spectrum, tahan air, dan transparan, yang membuat Kulit tubuh anda terasa dingin dan bersinar. Sunscreen mist yang ringan, mudah menyerap, dan menyegarkan ini dilengkapi dengan SPF 50+, vitamin C dan derivatif Vitamin E sebagai pelindung Kulit dan antioksidan aktif yang terdepan. Formula berkinerja tinggi yang digunakan dapat melindungi kulit dari sinar UVA, UVB, dan IRA, serta efek berbahaya paparan sinar matahari.', 1, 'https://www.soco.id/cdn-cgi/image/w=73,format=auto,dpr=1.45/https://images.soco.id/5fa75c81-7c75-4606-b3a6-aa4309257107-image-0-1626428175170\r'),
(259, 5, ' Dew It Dew It In The Morning Face Sun Stick ', 'https://www.sociolla.com/sunscreen/59157-dew-it-in-the-morning-face-sun-stick', 'DEW IT', 'Rp 195.000', 'Khawatir akan bintik hitam dan Kulit kusam? Perkenalkan Dew It in the Morning Face Sun Stick. Dilengkapi dengan SPF 50+ dan PA ++++, formula yang cepat meresap, non-komedogenik, than air dan keringat, memberikan proteksi berkinerja tinggi terhadap sinar UVA, UVB, dan IRA, serta mendukung Kulit dari photoaging dan dehidrasi. Dengan tekstur super ringan, mudah untuk menyatu dengan kulit, tidak ada white-cast, dan memberikan anda tampilan yang cerah, halus, dan tidak berminyak untuk penampilan yang cantik dan DEWY. RAIN OR SHINE, DEW IT IN THE MORNING!\"', 1, 'https://www.soco.id/cdn-cgi/image/w=73,format=auto,dpr=1.45/https://images.soco.id/6acda30c-5c78-4dfe-8241-f5bcacbad552-image-0-1626428007243\r'),
(260, 5, 'DEW IT On The Go - Sunscreen Mist', 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/product/detail/on-the-go-sunscreen-mist', 'DEW IT', 'Rp 220.000', 'Afraid of sun damage and unwanted sunburns? Meet your hands-free nourishing broad-spectrum transparent sunscreen that leaves your body with a cooling glow. Complete with SPF 50+, this lightweight, quick absorbing mist is water and sweat resistant providing high-performance protection from UVA, UVB, IRA rays and other harmful effects of sun exposure. Simply spray, sun, DEW it on the go!', 1, 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/assets/uploads/products/thumbs/800x800/DewIt_OnTheGo_SunScreenMist_1-removebg-preview.png\r'),
(261, 5, 'DEW IT In The Morning Face Sun Stick', 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/product/detail/in-the-morning-face-sun-stick', 'DEW IT', 'Rp 195.000', 'Afraid of dark spots and dull skin? Introducing Dew It In The Morning Face Sun Stick complete with SPF 50+ and PA++++. This fast absorbing, non-comedogenic, water and sweat-resistant formula provides high-performance protection from UVA, UVB, and IRA rays and supports skin from photo-aging and dehydration. With super light-weight texture that is easy-to-blend, it gives you a clear, no white-cast, non greasy feel for a beautiful, dewy look. Rain or shine, Dew It in the morning!', 1, 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/assets/uploads/products/thumbs/800x800/DewIt_-_In_The_Morning_Face_Sun_Stick_1-removebg-preview.png\r'),
(262, 2, 'DR JART V7 Pink Toning 50ml', 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/product/detail/v7-pink-toning-50ml', 'DR JART', 'Rp 685.000', 'What it is: A vitamin-enriched lightweight cream that brightens, soothes and moisturises tired, dull-looking skin tone. What it does: Dr.Jart+ patent complex, Rosy Lightâ„¢ revitalises your skin, leaving it hydrated and glowing.', 0, 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/assets/uploads/products/thumbs/800x800/jual_Dr_jart_v7_pink_toning_50_ml.JPG\r'),
(263, 2, 'DR JART V7 Toner 120g', 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/product/detail/v7-toner-120g', 'DR JART', 'Rp 515.000', 'What it is: A vitamin brightening toner that clears and brightens the skin tone with a vitamin keratin care solution. What it does: It provides not only brightening care with 7 Vitamin complex, but daliy keratin care with acidic solution (AHA, PHA, and Natural BHA) that improves skin turnover and makes skin clear and firmed.', 0, 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/assets/uploads/products/thumbs/800x800/jual_dr_jart_V7_Toner.JPG\r'),
(264, 2, 'DR JART Ceramidin Liquid Moisturizing Toner ', 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/product/detail/ceramidin-liquid-moisturizing-toner-150ml', 'DR JART', 'Rp 550.000', 'Ceramidin Liquid merupakan sebuah pelembab cair yang mengandung ceramides untuk memperkuat pelindung lapisan kulit dan dapat terserap hingga ke dalam lapisan kulit dengan sempurna. Gunakanlah secara teratur untuk mendapatkan semua manfaatnya dengan maksimal. Manfaat Pelembab cair ini berfungsi untuk melindungi lapisan kulit, mengencangkan kulit dan mencegah kulit dari iritasi setelah dibersihkan. Krimnya dapat terserap secara sempurna hingga ke lapisan kulit.', 0, 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/assets/uploads/products/thumbs/800x800/Cera_Liquid_Allure-removebg-preview.png\r'),
(265, 4, 'DR JART Vital Hydra Solution Biome Essence with Blue Shot 50ml ', 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/product/detail/vital-hydra-solution-biome-essence-with-blue-shot-50ml', 'DR JART', 'Rp 275.000', 'A hydrating essence that instantly calms skin. Perfect for hypersensitive skin, this hydrating essence improves your skin tone and texture while recovering sensitive skin to healthy, hydrated skin by Normalising microbiomes.', 0, 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/assets/uploads/products/thumbs/800x800/Jual_DR.JART%2B_Vital_Hydra_Solution_essence_50ml_2.jpg\r'),
(266, 2, 'DR JART CTRL-A Teatreement Toner ', 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/product/detail/ctrl-a-teatreement-toner', 'DR JART', 'Rp 515.000', 'Watery purifying toner that controls the excessive sebum and balances skin pH', 0, 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/assets/uploads/products/thumbs/800x800/teatreement_toner.png\r'),
(267, 4, 'DR JART Cicapair Serum 30ml ', 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/product/detail/cicapair-serum-30ml', 'DR JART', 'Rp 525.000', 'Suitable for even the most sensitive skin types, Cicapair Serum by Dr. Jart soothes and repairs skin while prepping it for moisturiser to reveal a visibly healthy-looking complexion. Like the entire Cicapairâ„¢ Collection, itâ€™s infused with soothing Centella Asiatica, or tiger grass, an active ingredient used for generations to restore and support damaged skin and inflammation. Suggested Use After cleansing skin, apply a moderate amount of serum. It will change from green-to-beige to correct redness.', 0, 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/assets/uploads/products/thumbs/800x800/5c307ffed18729008344ed4583907a1a_1523860390_7571.png\r'),
(268, 4, 'DR JART NEW Ceramidin Serum 40ml ', 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/product/detail/new-ceramidin-serum-40ml', 'DR JART', 'Rp 600.000', 'With 5 kinds of ceramide to create a moisture barrier to retain moisture for a long time. Dermatologically tested. Suitable for sensitive skin.', 0, 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/assets/uploads/products/thumbs/800x800/jual_dr_jart_ceramidin_serum1.jpg\r'),
(269, 4, 'DR JART Vital Hydra Solution Capsule Ampoule (2ml x 6)', 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/product/detail/vital-hydra-solution-capsule-ampoule-2ml-x-6', 'DR JART', 'Rp 260.000', 'Ultimate hydrating ampoule in a capsule that provides abundant hydration to the skin with 5-HA complex and seaweed secretion extract. What it does: 6,000ppm(0.6%) of 5-Hyaluronic acid complex. Undiluted pure hyaluronic acid of low and high molecular weights filling inside the skin drop by drop! â€¢ High molecular: makes natural dewy skin â€¢ Medium molecular: fills hydrating power under the skin â€¢ Small molecular: provides deep hydrate What\'s included: 2ml x 6 capsules', 0, 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/assets/uploads/products/thumbs/800x800/Jual_DR.JART%2B_Vital_Hydra_Solution_Capsule_Ampoule_1.jpg\r'),
(270, 4, 'DR JART V7 Serum 50ml ', 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/product/detail/v7-serum-50ml', 'DR JART', 'Rp 635.000', 'What it is: A vitamin-enriched brightening serum that evens out the skin tone and improves skin vitality. What it does: This serum intensively treats dark spots and improves skin elasticity to make the skin healthy and illuminated.', 0, 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/assets/uploads/products/thumbs/800x800/jual_Dr_jart_v7_serum-u.JPG\r'),
(271, 2, 'DR JART V7 Emulsion 120g', 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/product/detail/v7-emulsion-120g', 'DR JART', 'Rp 535.000', 'What it is: A brightening emulsion that moisturises Dry and rough skin What it does: This emulsion brings ultimate moisture balance and firms the skin texture. Its gel texture is gently absorbed into the skin leaving it feeling fresh.', 0, 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/assets/uploads/products/thumbs/800x800/jual_Dr_jart_v7_emulsion.jpg\r'),
(272, 3, 'ELSHE SKIN Acne Night Cream Treatment', 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/product/detail/acne-night-cream-treatment', 'ELSHE SKIN', 'Rp 92.000', 'Dengan Formula Salicylic Acid,Lactic Acid,Multi Fruit AHA,dan bahan anti acne untuk merawat kulit wajah yang berjerawat, mengurangi minyak berlebih,dan membantu mencegah timbulnya jerawat.', 0, 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/assets/uploads/products/thumbs/800x800/acne_night_treatment1.png\r'),
(273, 2, 'Elsheskin Brightening Refresh Toner', 'https://www.sociolla.com/toner/10473-brightening-refresh-toner', 'ELSHE SKIN', 'Rp 65.000', 'Penyegar dengan kandungan Glutathione, Vitamin C, Grapee Seed Extract, dan Arbutin bermaanfaat untuk mengembalikan pH dan kelembaban alami kulit setelah proses pembersihan, sekaligus mencerahkan kulit.', 0, 'https://www.soco.id/cdn-cgi/image/w=73,format=auto,dpr=1.45/https://images.soco.id/29c40650-6606-4748-88b4-6881deea3e60-image-0-1631089755563\r'),
