(576, 4, 'KIEHLS Hydro Plumping Re-Texturizing Serum Concentrate (50ml)', 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/product/detail/hydro-plumping-re-texturizing-serum-concentrate-50ml', 'KIEHL\'S ', 'Rp 935.000', 'Krim pelembap yang memperbaiki kekenyalan kulit Memanfaatkan teknologi masa depan cairan-ke-serum untuk melembapkan kulit secara intensif, sampai lapisan terdalam Secara klinis terbukti membantu memperbaiki tanda-tanda dehidrasi yang disebabkan oleh bertambahnya usia Kulit yang kenyal dan awet muda, memperhalus penampilan garis halus dan tekstur yang kasar Diformulasikan dengan 15% Glycerin berbasis tanaman yang ampuh dan ekstrak daun shiso', 0, 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/assets/uploads/products/thumbs/800x800/Hydro-Plumping_Re-Texturizing_Serum_Concentrate.jpg\r'),
(577, 5, 'KIEHLS Ultra Light Daily UV Defense SPF 50 PA++++ with Anti Pollution (30ml) ', 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/product/detail/ultra-light-daily-uv-defense-spf-50-pa-with-anti-pollution-30ml', 'KIEHL\'S', 'Rp 610.000', 'A lightweight facial sunscreen with SPF 50 PA++++ to protect against pollution and the first signs of aging. Hydrate and help protect skin from the early signs of aging with our lightweight facial sunscreen with broad spectrum SPF 50 PA++++. With advanced UVA/UVB technology and pollution protection, our formula helps defend against UV rays, while Cellulospheres protects against pollution and free radicals. Our daily, non-comedogenic sunscreen provides all-day hydration, absorbs quickly and leaves a matte finish. Helps protect skin from environmental aggressors including UVA/UVB rays and pollution which can cause the first signs of aging Lightweight formula absorbs quickly and leaves skin with a matte finish Formulated with advanced UVA/UVB technology and pollution protection Dermatologist-tested for safety Non-comedogenic Suitable for all skin types, including sensitive skin', 0, 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/assets/uploads/products/thumbs/800x800/ultra_light_daily_uv_defense.jpg\r'),
(578, 4, 'KINDY GLOW Powerful Daisy â€“ Serum ', 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/product/detail/powerful-daisy-serum-mencerahkan-dan-melembutkan', 'KINDY GLOW', ' Rp 68.200', 'Kindy Glow Powerful Daisy adalah Brightening dan Glow Serum yang berfungsi untuk mencerahkan, meratakan warna kulit, menyamarkan flek hitam dan bekas jerawat, menyamarkan kemerahan pada kulit, menenangkan inflamasi, menghidrasi kulit wajah, memudarkan tampilan pori-pori, melembabkan kulit, dan melembutkan kulit. Diperkaya dengan 7 bahan aktif mencerahkan dan melembutkan: - Daisy Flower - 5% Niacinamide, - Glutathione, - Glabridin, - Squalane, - Glycyrrhiza Glabra Root Extract (Licorice Root Extract), - Dipotassium Glycyrrhizinate (Licorice).', 1, 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/assets/uploads/products/thumbs/800x800/Powerful_Daisy.png\r'),
(579, 3, 'Dear Klairs Freshly Juiced Vitamin E Mask ', 'https://www.sociolla.com/face-cream-lotion/9657-freshly-juiced-vitamin-e-mask', 'KLAIRS', 'Rp 390.000', 'Perlindungan maskimal untuk kulitmu sepanjang hari!', 1, 'https://www.soco.id/cdn-cgi/image/w=73,format=auto,dpr=1.45/https://images.soco.id/90004125604-1600852158956.png\r'),
(580, 4, 'KLAIRS Freshly Juiced Vitamin Drop 35ml', 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/product/detail/freshly-juiced-vitamin-drop-35ml', 'KLAIRS', 'Rp 297.500', 'Description Klairs Freshly Juiced Vitamin Drop adalah vitamin untuk wajah yang bermanfaat untuk memberikan energi dan meremajakan kulit dengan kandungan vitamin C murninya. Aplikasi secara rutin akan menyegarkan kulit yang kusam dan mengecilkan pori-pori. Suitable for : Semua jenis kulit', 0, 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/assets/uploads/products/thumbs/800x800/Klairs_Freshly_Juiced_Vitamin_Drop_35ml.jpg\r'),
(581, 4, 'KLAIRS Fundamental Watery Oil Drop', 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/product/detail/fundamental-watery-oil-drop', 'KLAIRS', 'Rp 430.000', 'Terbuat dengan utama Green Tea dr Pulau Jeju dan Peptide, serum ini yang kaya akan kandungan Anti-oxidant sehingga dapat membantu untuk meregenerasi, menutrisi dan melembabkan kulit', 0, 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/assets/uploads/products/thumbs/800x800/Klairs_Fundamental_Watery_Oil_Drop.jpg\r'),
(582, 3, 'KLAIRS Midnight Blue Calming Cream 60ml', 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/product/detail/midnight-blue-calming-cream-60ml', 'KLAIRS', 'Rp 450.000', 'A gentle spot treatment cream that provides comfort to rapidly calm & soothe sensitivity. Powered by nature, its star ingredients are Guaiazulene, a natural component extracted from chamomile oil, which carries powerful skin calming abilities, and Centella Asiatica, which helps hydrate and relieve redness. Available in double the amount! That\'s right, 60ml worth of calming cream packaged in a tube that is convenient to carry on-the-go.', 0, 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/assets/uploads/products/thumbs/800x800/Midnight_Blue_Calming_Cream_60_ml.jpg\r'),
(583, 3, 'KLAIRS Midnight Blue Calming Cream 30ml', 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/product/detail/midnight-blue-calming-cream-30ml', 'KLAIRS', 'Rp 360.000', 'A little blue withÂ a big impact. If moisturizing just wasnâ€™t enough for your sensitive skin, meetÂ the Dear,Klairs Midnight Blue Calming Cream to protect your skin from irritation and stress. This little blue cream helps to calm and strengthen the barriers ofÂ extremely sensitive skin. When usedÂ with the â€œRich Moistâ€ line, it works rapidly to soothe and regulate irritation from heat or sebum. Why a blue cream? Calming with Guaiazulene With herbal ingredients extracted from Chamomile, itâ€™s natural dark purple color gives the cream a blue hue and effectively calmsÂ inflammation of damaged skin tissueÂ andÂ regeneratesÂ skin cells. Containing 0.03% (similar to amounts contained inÂ ointments currently on the market), Japanese clinical trials demonstrated its effectiveness onÂ 89.7% ofÂ sunburns, 60.6% ofÂ eczema, and 86.5% ofÂ ulcerative skin diseases. Â It is the main raw material in burn ointments. Healing with Centella Asiatica Extract A plant native to Madagascar, it is also known as â€˜tiger grassâ€™ and often used in cosmetics as â€˜Centella Asiatica.â€™ It is the primary ingredient in ointments and helps toÂ regenerate damaged skin and prevents scarring.', 0, 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/assets/uploads/products/thumbs/800x800/Midnight_Blue_Calming_Cream_30_ml.jpg\r'),
(584, 3, 'KLAIRS Freshly Juiced Vitamin E Mask Miniature', 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/product/detail/freshly-juiced-vitamin-e-mask-miniature', 'KLAIRS', 'Rp 120.000', 'Dapat membantu untuk mencerahkan, menghidrasi, melembabkan, mengurangi garis-garis halus & keriput dan memperbaiki texture kulit', 0, 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/assets/uploads/products/thumbs/800x800/Freshly_Juiced_Vitamin_E_Mask_Miniature_15ml.png\r'),
(585, 2, 'KLAIRS Daily Skin Hydrating Water', 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/product/detail/daily-skin-hydrating-water', 'KLAIRS ', 'Rp 400.000', 'Daily Skin Hydrating Toner merupakan toner pelembab seperti air tanpa viskositas, mengandung 45% Green Tea Water dengan efek menenangkan dan antioksidasi untuk menenangkan kulit. Toner ringan ini dapat digunakan setiap hari di musim apa pun pada semua jenis kulit karena teksturnya yang encer akan cepat terserap ke dalam kulit. Ini juga cocok digunakan sebagai toner untuk membasuh wajah Anda pada langkah pertama rutinitas perawatan kulit Anda untuk meratakan tekstur kulit, dan penyerapannya yang cepat memungkinkan Anda melapisinya beberapa kali. Dianjurkan untuk orang yang lebih menyukai toner ringan dan menyegarkan.', 1, 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/assets/uploads/products/thumbs/800x800/Daily_Skin_Hydrating_Water.png\r'),
(586, 2, 'KLAIRS Daily Skin Softening Water', 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/product/detail/daily-skin-softening-water', 'KLAIRS ', 'Rp 400.000', 'Daily Skin Softening Water merupakan toner exofoliasi seperti air dengan iritasi rendah dan tanpa viskositas. Dapat dengan mudah merawat sel kulit mati setiap hari dengan toner ini karena mengandung ekstrak tebu, exfoliant alami, dan sedikit (0,15%) asam sitrat yang menyebabkan iritasi paling rendah di antara AHA. Toner juga mengandung 45% air mentimun yang memberikan hidrasi yang kaya dan sensasi menyegarkan untuk menenangkan kulit kering yang mungkin disebabkan oleh pengelupasan. Dianjurkan untuk jenis kulit yang menderita sel kulit mati dan komedo putih yang berlebihan, dan juga untuk kulit yang hipersensitif karena tidak menyebabkan iritasi atau lengket.', 0, 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/assets/uploads/products/thumbs/800x800/Daily_Skin_Softening_Water.png\r'),
(587, 2, 'KLAIRS Supple Preparation UNSCENTED Facial Toner', 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/product/detail/supple-preparation-unscented-facial-toner', 'KLAIRS', 'Rp 310.000', 'The most important thing for Klairs is that we are bringing quality products to our customers. Therefore, the brand team at Klairs HQ came together to develop one of Klairs most-widely loved and popular toner with an unscented version, meaning no essential oil. Since some of our customers were unable to try the original toner due to the essential oil, this newly formulated unscented toner will now give them the opportunity to try it without a worry. Main Functions and Differences, Fast absorbing, Lightweight texture, Low irritation, Vegan-friendly. The toner is lightweight, moisturizing for all skin types, including those with Oily skin; it is free of essential oils and any other harsh ingredients. Its light gel-like consistency seeps into skin to make the skin less Dry and more smooth and plump with consistent use. This toner has a star studded ingredient list perfect for all skin types, and features a soothing blend of plant based extracts, along with the hydrating ingredient hyaluronic acid, and the soothing centella asiatica. As mentioned previously, the main difference between the two are that the unscented packaging has changed from a brown bottle to a transparent bottle to match the theme of the no essential oils. In addition, there is a beautiful purple and silver color theme for a newer, fresher, and sleeker feel to the product.', 1, 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/assets/uploads/products/thumbs/800x800/Supple_Preparation_Unscented_Toner.jpg\r'),
(588, 2, 'KLAIRS Supple Preparation Facial Toner 180ml', 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/product/detail/supple-preparation-facial-toner-180ml', 'KLAIRS', 'Rp 300.000', 'Klairs Supple Preparation Facial Toner adalah toner yang tidak menyebabkan iritasi, sekaligus dapat meremajakan dan menghidrasi kulit. Formulanya cepat menyerap dengan level pH yang seimbang. Suitable for : Semua jenis kulit', 1, 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/assets/uploads/products/thumbs/800x800/klairs_supple_prepation_toner.jpg\r'),
(589, 2, 'KLAIRS Unscented Toner Miniature ', 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/product/detail/unscented-toner-miniature', 'KLAIRS ', 'Rp 105.000', 'The unscented toner is the essential oil-free version of the original toner. The irritation-free natural essential oils were removed from the original toner to accommodate customers who prefer non-scented products.', 1, 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/assets/uploads/products/thumbs/800x800/Klairs_Unscented_Toner_Miniature.png\r'),
(590, 4, 'KLAIRS Rich Moist Soothing Serum 80ml ', 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/product/detail/rich-moist-soothing-serum-80ml', 'KLAIRS', 'Rp 330.000', 'DescriptionÂ  Introducing the best skin care serum, Klairs Rich Moist Soothing Serum ! A magical soothing lotion for sensitive skin, Klairs Rich Moist Soothing Serum ! Get your most gorgeous and healthiest looking skin yet ! Add the Klairs Rich Moist Soothing Serum lotion for sensitive skin to your daily cleansing, toning and moisturizing routine ! Replenish your skins moisture levels making your skin look soft, smooth, more radiant and younger looking! Give your tired, dehydrated, sensitive, Dry skin the drink of water it deserves with Klairs Rich Moist Soothing Serum !* Features Why do we need to use a serum lotion for sensitive skin? Serums, are considered to be the most important step in any skincare routine. Serums contain smaller molecules with higher concentrates of beneficial ingredients compared to regular moisturizers. Serums are intensively infused with higher concentrates of active ingredients that can penetrate deeper into the skin, delivering more targeted results. Serums fit perfectly into every skin care routine to provide you with the optimal results your skin needs, no matter your skin type! Did you know? Serums are also a great alternative for makeup primers! Use a serum to prime your skin before applying your skin makeup! Get the most smooth and soft looking makeup application with all the benefits of serum! Rehydrate fine lines, smooth over the appearance of pores and create a soft skin surface that is ready for makeup application. Klairs supports 4 main directives in all their products to make you feel safe and comfortable about using the brand!! Klairs serum lotion for sensitive skin strives to provide you with a Rich Moist Soothing Serum that is most beneficial to you and your skin by providing a product that is: 1. No animal testing 2. Alcohol free 3. No paraben 4. No Artificial Coloring 5. Eco friendly', 0, 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/assets/uploads/products/thumbs/800x800/Rich_Moist_Soothing_Serum.jpg\r');
