(1025, 2, 'The Face Shop White Seed Brightening Toner', 'https://ms-thefaceshop.eraspace.com/product/white-seed-brightening-toner', 'THE FACE SHOP', 'Rp 269.100', 'White Seed Brightening Toner Toner yang mengandung White Lupin Seed dan White Daisy. White Seed Brightening Series memberikan perawatan yang mencerahkan kulit mulai dari toner, lotion, serum, krim, dan pembersih untuk Anda. White Seed Brightening Toner berfungsi sebagai penyeimbang ph yang melembabkan dan mencerahan kulit secara merata. Bebas dari zat kimia berbahaya seperti paraben. Ingredients: White Lupine Seed, White Daisy, White Willow Bark', 1, 'https://cdn.eraspace.com/pub/media/catalog/product/w/h/white-seed-brightening-toner-3.jpg\r'),
(1026, 3, 'The Face Shop Yehwadam Artemisia Soothing Moisturizing Emulsion', 'https://ms-thefaceshop.eraspace.com/product/yehwadam-artemisia-soothing-moisturizing-emulsion', 'THE FACE SHOP', 'Rp 375.000', 'Yehwadam Artemisia Soothing Moisturizing Emulsion Melembapkan + Menenangkan Kulit Bermasalah', 1, 'https://cdn.eraspace.com/pub/media/catalog/product/y/e/yehwadam_artemisia_soothing_moisturizing_emulsion_4.jpg\r'),
(1027, 4, 'TISHA [TISHA] AC7 SPOT SERUM PHYTOSILICA Injection 4ml ', 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/product/detail/tisha-ac7-spot-serum-phytosilica-injection-4ml', 'TISHA', 'Rp 240.000', 'The AC7 is a brightening, moisturizing and acne-improving skin care. It does not consist of any harmful ingredients. Consists of Niacinamide, 11 types of Dyropteris Crassirhizoma Extracts, Phytosilica, Salicylic Acid, Tea Tree oils, Luffa Cynlindrica extracts, Coptis Chinensis Root Extract, Bacopa Monniera Extract, Polyglutamic Acid and Phellodendron Amurense Bark Extract. The AC7 is not an extensive-use product. A fundamental solution for all your troubled needs. Sanitary way of use to remove your skin problems. (Finger wrap etc) Brightens, moisturizes, improves acne problems and skin troubles. Focuses on the point where the product is placed and effectively takes care of it. Use after your night face wash and with the finger wrap, massage the troubled area 7 times going up and down, left and right etc. No harmful ingredients Consists of Niacinamide (known for itâ€™s brightening effects) and 11 kinds of Dryopteris Crassirhizoma Extract that solves all acne problems with the help of Phytosilica.', 1, 'https://www.beautyhaul.com/assets/uploads/products/thumbs/800x800/fccb486a7b2db91c1c05e6750d34d470.jpg\r'),
(1028, 5, 'TRILOGY Rosehip Multishield Moisturizer SPF15 ', 'https://www.sociolla.com/sunscreen/16644-rosehip-multishield-moisturizer-spf15', 'TRILOGY', 'Rp 650.000', 'pelembab yang berguna juga sebagai sunscreen. Memberikan kelembapan yang seimbang untuk kulit wajah dan melindungi wajah dari efek UVA, UVB dan sinar biru. Cocok untuk semua jenis kulit', 1, 'https://cnfstore.com/pub/media/catalog/product/cache/2a62a76a24179803c442e74cd57fe434/c/f/cf013720.jpg\r'),
