(1138, 1, 'YOU Golden Age Deep Cleansing Facial Wash', 'https://shopee.co.id/YOU-Golden-Age-Deep-Cleansing-Facial-Wash-100g-Deep-Pore-Cleansing-Removes--i.72375863.3711966673?sp_atk=30a4f57c-0fbc-4aa1-a933-4cf11b1cc912', 'YOU', 'Rp 55.000', 'Golden Age Deep Cleansing Facial Wash diformulasikan dengan ekstrak Buah Delima dan Lactic Acid yang mampu membersihkan sisa makeup dan pori-pori secara mendalam sehingga kulit terasa lebih lembut dan kenyal. ', 1, 'http://image.femaledaily.com/dyn/640/images/prod-pics/product_1579753308_GOLDEN_AGE_800x800.jpg\r');
